macro_item.script:
-_RunScript ( C = Rhino.ViewCamera() T = Rhino.ViewTarget() if (StepSize = 0) then StepSize = 0.05
Cnew = C Tnew = T
Dx = T(0) - C(0) Dy = T(1) - C(1)
Dist = Sqr(Dx*Dx + Dy*Dy)
Cnew(2) = Cnew(2) - Dist * StepSize Tnew(2) = Tnew(2) - Dist * StepSize
Rhino.ViewCameraTarget Rhino.CurrentView(), Cnew, Tnew )

macro_item.script:
-_RunPythonScript (
import rhinoscriptsyntax as rs import scriptcontext as sc import math
StepSize = 0.05 if sc.sticky.has_key('WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE'): StepSize = sc.sticky['WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE']
NewStepSize = rs.RealBox("New step sizefactor", StepSize) if NewStepSize is not None: StepSize = NewStepSize sc.sticky['WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE'] = StepSize )

! -_RunPythonScript ( import rhinoscriptsyntax as rs import scriptcontext as sc import math
StepSize = 0.02 if sc.sticky.has_key('WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE'): StepSize = sc.sticky['WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE']
C = rs.ViewCamera() T = rs.ViewTarget()
Cnew = C Tnew = T
Dx = T[0] - C[0] Dy = T[1] - C[1]
Cnew[0] = Cnew[0] + Dx * StepSize Cnew[1] = Cnew[1] + Dy * StepSize Tnew[0] = Tnew[0] + Dx * StepSize Tnew[1] = Tnew[1] + Dy * StepSize
rs.ViewCameraTarget(rs.CurrentView(), Cnew, Tnew) )

StepSize = 0.05 if sc.sticky.has_key('WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE'): StepSize = sc.sticky['WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE']
C = rs.ViewCamera() T = rs.ViewTarget()
Cnew = C Tnew = T
Dx = T[0] - C[0] Dy = T[1] - C[1]
Cnew[0] = Cnew[0] - Dy * StepSize Cnew[1] = Cnew[1] + Dx * StepSize Tnew[0] = Tnew[0] - Dy * StepSize Tnew[1] = Tnew[1] + Dx * StepSize
rs.ViewCameraTarget(rs.CurrentView(), Cnew, Tnew) )

StepSize = 0.05 if sc.sticky.has_key('WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE'): StepSize = sc.sticky['WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE']
C = rs.ViewCamera() T = rs.ViewTarget()
Cnew = C Tnew = T
Dx = T[0] - C[0] Dy = T[1] - C[1]
Cnew[0] = Cnew[0] + Dy * StepSize Cnew[1] = Cnew[1] - Dx * StepSize Tnew[0] = Tnew[0] + Dy * StepSize Tnew[1] = Tnew[1] - Dx * StepSize
rs.ViewCameraTarget(rs.CurrentView(), Cnew, Tnew) )

-_RunPythonScript (
import rhinoscriptsyntax as rs import scriptcontext as sc import math
StepSize = 0.05 if sc.sticky.has_key('WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE'): StepSize = sc.sticky['WALKABOUT_STEPSIZE']
C = rs.ViewCamera() T = rs.ViewTarget()
Cnew = C Tnew = T
Dx = T[0] - C[0] Dy = T[1] - C[1]
Dist = math.sqrt(Dx*Dx + Dy*Dy)
Cnew[2] = Cnew[2] - Dist * StepSize Tnew[2] = Tnew[2] - Dist * StepSize
rs.ViewCameraTarget (rs.CurrentView(), Cnew, Tnew) )
